_sText:
a spawn room for multiplayer roundless gamemodes, such as bhop, kz, xc, mg courses etc.

intended for gamemodes with no player collisions.

it contains 50 ct spawns in a black room, and instantly teleports the player to the tele1 teleport destination. which is supposed to be the first stage of your map.

the prefab exists so you don't have to stack so many spawn points in your map's first stage, mapping is cleaner this way.
